name: Coban Rondo Love Story
description: Coban Rondo is one of the names of waterfalls in Indonesia. the word "rondo" means widow. It tells the story of a newlywed named Dewi Anjarwati and Raden Baron Kusuma who are traveling to Mount Anjasmoro. In Java, it is believed that newlyweds who have just married are prohibited from traveling far. On the way, they met Joko Lelono who wanted to take the wife of Raden Baron Kusuma. the husband told Dewi Anjarwati to run away to find a place with a waterfall. the fight between Raden Baron Kusuma and Joko Lelono was inevitable. in the end they both died. So that Dewi Anjarwati who was waiting for Raden Baron Kusuma's arrival at the waterfall became a widow.
